lines.text:
[to Laurie after she has killed Kay with her shotgun]
Did it bring Bonnie back? You have the rest of your life to think about that now.

[to Kay in the final showdown, Kay is visibly frightened of her]
And you're the ONLY one left!

[Kay and Miss Dice have discovered another one of Kay's henchwomen dead in the shower]
What's going on, Kay?

[screaming in anguish]
How the fuck do I know!

[to Laurie after she's put in prison]
I didn't mean to kill him! Don't let them keep me in here, Laurie!

[as she's beating Bonnie in the shower]
You're a long way from home, Goldilocks!

[after she and her henchwomen have dumped Bonnie off the ledge]
Sayonara, sweet lips!

[to Laurie after the confrontation in the gym]
Curtains to you, Bambi!
